<i>adverb</i>: 도도히 [도ː도히], 거들먹거들먹 [거들먹꺼들먹] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>도도히 [도ː도히]</dt><br>
<dd>haughtily; arrogantly</dd><br>
<dd>잘난 체하며 매우 거만하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With an attitude of being arrogant and putting on airs.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>거들먹거들먹 [거들먹꺼들먹]</dt><br>
<dd>haughtily; lordly; overbearingly</dd><br>
<dd>잘난 체하며 자꾸 건방지게 행동하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of someone behaving affectedly and insolently.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>